# Sprint 228 TDD red-state log

Date: 2026-05-07.

## Process

Generator captured the red→green TDD trajectory by writing the
13 new vitest cases for the Sprint 228 `describe("Sprint 228 — Indexes
tab functional", …)` block FIRST, then making the implementation
changes pass. The intermediate "red" output below records the canonical
